rm our own art-into-life experiments within contemporary political art. Deineka figures in this study not as a singular master, in the spirit of a traditional monograph, but as a limit case of the system he inhabited and helped to create.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aArtzSoviet Union. 0aSocialist realism. 7aART / General.2bisacsh  aSoviet art, Socialist Realism, Aleksandr Deineka.40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226827179423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780226827179/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles